dct_title_s: Square Bay to Matha Strait including Adelaide Island (Raster Image)
dct_description_sm: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. "From British Admiralty and Argentine charts to 1984." Includes compilation diagram. Georeferenced nautical chart. Map no. 29141.
This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
